Begin Row: k1, (k1, yo, k1) in next stitch*
Repeat: k5 wrapping yarn twice for each stitch, (k1. yo, k1, yo, k1) in next stitch
End Row: k5 wrapping yarn twice for each stitch, (k1, yo, k1) in next stitch, k1

Repeat: sl 5 wyif dropping extra wraps, then insert left needle back into these 5 long stitches and p5-tog; k5

Begin Row: k1, k3 wrapping yarn twice for each stitch*
Repeat: (k1, yo, k1, yo, k1) in next stitch, k5 wrapping yarn twice for each stitch
End Row: (k1, yo, k1, yyo, k1) in next stitch, k3 wrapping yarn twice for each stitch, k1

Begin Row: k1, sl 3 wyif dropping extra wraps, insert left needle into these 3 stitches and p3-tog*
Repeat: k5, sl 5 wyif dropping extra wraps, then insert left needle back into these 5 long stitches and p5-tog
End Row: k5, sl 3 wyif, dropping extra wraps, insert needle into these 3 stitches and p3-tog, k1
